platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: おもしろおかしいモンスターをつくろう

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: DNAパズルでクリーチャーが変身

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Genetics can be tricky to explain, even for us so-called adults. DNA Play gently introduces kids to the concepts of cellular building blocks, letting youngsters create goofy monsters and mutate them on the fly by swapping around their genetic code. It’s great simply as a charming, colorful puzzle game to entertain the little ones, but has the added bonus of educating and enlightening budding young scientists.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Tinker with genetics to create cute monsters.
Jouez avec l’ADN et créez d’adorables petits monstres.
